    "Section \"Conclusion\" concludes our paper.",
    "The DIR forecasting method we employed leverages the power of an ensemble comprising three distinct machine learning models.",
    "This ensemble consists of a CatBoost model, a SVM, and a LSTM model.",
    "Each of these models possesses unique characteristics that, when combined, demonstrate good performance in predicting the DIR in Brazil and Peru.",
    "The first model in our ensemble is CatBoost, a gradient boosting algorithm that excels in handling categorical features and generating accurate predictions."
